OL,6,FAn asylum seeker who tried to cut his
OL,7,Fwife's head off and left her to bleed
OL,8,Fto death on their children's bedroom
OL,9,Ffloor has been jailed for at least 19
OL,10,Fyears and six months.
OL,12,FWahib Albaradan, 37, used two knives
OL,13,Fand a razor in a "prolonged,
OL,14,Fpersistent and frenzied" attack on
OL,15,FSalam Alshara, 27, at their home in
OL,16,FDewsbury, West Yorkshire, in November
OL,17,F2023.
