OL,6,FHe then removed any phones that could
OL,7,Fbe used to call for help from the
OL,8,Fhouse and fled the scene, being
OL,9,Farrested the next morning after a
OL,10,Flarge police manhunt.
OL,12,FOn Tuesday Albaradan, who pleaded
OL,13,Fguilty to murder, was jailed for life
OL,14,Fwith a minimum term of 19 years and
OL,15,Fsix months by a judge who said he was
OL,16,Fa "jealous and controlling husband who
OL,17,Fbullied and manipulated (Ms Alshara)".
