OL,6,FLeeds Crown Court heard the couple had
OL,7,Fmarried in their native Syria and had
OL,8,Ffour children but Albaradan, who was a
OL,9,Ffarmer, had been an "angry and
OL,10,Fjealous" husband, leading Ms Alshara
OL,11,Fto almost divorce him at one point
OL,12,Fbefore he convinced her and her
OL,13,F"loving family" that things would
OL,14,Fchange.
OL,16,FAlbaradan came to the UK in 2020 and
OL,17,FMs Alshara joined him in 2021, with a
OL,18,Fneighbour in Dewsbury saying she was
OL,19,F"timid and withdrawn" but "seemed
OL,20,Freally nice".
