OL,6,FProsecutor Nicholas Worsley KC said,
OL,7,Fin the months before the murder,
OL,8,FAlbaradan became increasingly paranoid
OL,9,Fthat Ms Alshara was talking to other
OL,10,Fmen and disapproved of her installing
OL,11,Fapps like WhatsApp on her phone,
OL,12,Fconvinced she was using them to have
OL,13,Fan affair and was "dishonouring" him.
OL,15,FHe confiscated her mobile phone, tried
OL,16,Fto get her to wear a niqab covering
OL,17,Fher face ` something the women in her
OL,18,Ffamily did not do ` and told her
OL,19,Fstories about a man who had killed his
OL,20,Fwife and only got a few days in
OL,21,Fprison, Mr Worsley said.
