OL,6,FAlbaradan later told a psychiatrist he
OL,7,Fhad tried to kill his wife by
OL,8,Fstrangling her on a previous occasion,
OL,9,Fand she told her sister she was
OL,10,Fworried he would "carry out his
OL,11,Fthreats and that something would
OL,12,Fhappen to her".
OL,14,FThe court heard on the day of the
OL,15,Fmurder, the couple argued again and Ms
OL,16,FAlshara may have told Albaradan she
OL,17,Fwas going to leave.
