OL,6,FAlbaradan attacked her with two
OL,7,Fkitchen knives before taking what
OL,8,Fappeared to be a razor from a drawer
OL,9,Fand slashing at her neck, slitting her
OL,10,Fthroat before leaving her to die.
OL,12,FA pathologist found Ms Alshara had at
OL,13,Fleast 20 sharp force injuries,
OL,14,Fincluding defensive injuries showing
OL,15,Fshe had fought for her life.
OL,17,FCCTV showed Albaradan walking barefoot
OL,18,Fthrough the streets of Ravensthorpe,
OL,19,Fin Dewsbury, at one point discarding
OL,20,Fhis bloodstained jogging bottoms in a
OL,21,Fgarden shed.
