OL,6,FThe court heard Albaradan has since
OL,7,Fbeen diagnosed with paranoid
OL,8,Fschizophrenia and told a psychiatrist
OL,9,Fhe believed Ms Alshara was talking to
OL,10,Fmen on social media and he would have
OL,11,Fkilled her if they were in Syria,
OL,12,Fadding: "That's our law."
OL,14,FHe also said nothing would have
OL,15,Fhappened to him because it "would have
OL,16,Fbeen an honour crime," Mr Worsley said.
